    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🍽️ About This Game – <i>Cosmic Café</i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are the new owner of the once-legendary <i>Cosmic Café</i>. With the previous owner missing and the galaxy ravaged by a ruthless corporate overlord, Take charge and restore the café to its former glory and discover the mystery behind your new and unexpected role.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🍽️ Manage &amp; Upgrade Your Café</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318190/extras/227d0d16e6f890d35a447206f7c0b4a8.poster.avif?t=1761419067\" width=800 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318190/extras/227d0d16e6f890d35a447206f7c0b4a8.webm?t=1761419067\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318190/extras/227d0d16e6f890d35a447206f7c0b4a8.mp4?t=1761419067\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Bring this forgotten café back to life with new machines, décor, and custom asteroid biomes. Upgrade your kitchen and cafe tools to serve up exotic dishes and premium services   </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🧭 Explore Biomes &amp; Gather Ingredients<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318190/extras/553e377311e39e73ccfe278f7cfebf0b.poster.avif?t=1761419067\" width=800 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318190/extras/553e377311e39e73ccfe278f7cfebf0b.webm?t=1761419067\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318190/extras/553e377311e39e73ccfe278f7cfebf0b.mp4?t=1761419067\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle your way through artificial biomes to collect rare alien ingredients for your menu.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🧪 Transform Your DNA &amp; Adapt<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318190/extras/10921eefea62bcb49cef79be63869a15.poster.avif?t=1761419067\" width=800 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318190/extras/10921eefea62bcb49cef79be63869a15.webm?t=1761419067\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318190/extras/10921eefea62bcb49cef79be63869a15.mp4?t=1761419067\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the Cafe's advanced technology to Harvest DNA from mutated lifeforms and transform yourself unlocking new forms!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >👽 Rescue and Serve your Customers<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318190/extras/1b68a94a60b8c65672586d721c03b193.poster.avif?t=1761419067\" width=800 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318190/extras/1b68a94a60b8c65672586d721c03b193.webm?t=1761419067\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318190/extras/1b68a94a60b8c65672586d721c03b193.mp4?t=1761419067\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Gecks, a once peaceful native species, have been taxed and brainwashed into servitude.  Rescue them and turn them into loyal café customers.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >⚖️ Fight Back Against the Galactic Revenue Service<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318190/extras/0288d7117497ab221f4d55af24d07030.poster.avif?t=1761419067\" width=800 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318190/extras/0288d7117497ab221f4d55af24d07030.webm?t=1761419067\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318190/extras/0288d7117497ab221f4d55af24d07030.mp4?t=1761419067\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Galactic Revenue Service will stop at nothing to shut you down. Master alien-level tax evasion and defend your cafe while uncovering the truth behind their grip on the universe.<br><br><u><strong>About the Developer</strong></u><br>I’m Michael, a solo game developer who began my journey as a 3D artist, collaborating with studios to craft unique art styles and immersive worlds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cosmic Café grew from my love of sci-fi, ’90s cartoons, and adventure into unknown worlds. Set in a bizarre, handcrafted space environment, it’s a world where creativity, chaos, and weird alien cuisine collide! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
